CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Osisko Development Corp is a gold mining company. It is focused on exploring and developing its mining assets, including the Cariboo and Bonanza Ledge II gold projects in British Columbia and the San Antonio gold project in Mexico. The Cariboo Gold Project mineral tenures cover around 2,071 square kilometres; along a strike length of 83 kilometres which includes several past producing placer and hard rock mines.
